1. *Saznao* sam da imamo slobodan dan.(I found out that we have a free day.)
2. On je *saznao* da je ona otišla.(He found out that she had left.)
3. Ona je *saznala* da mu je otac poginuo u ratu.(She found out that his father had died in a war.)
4. Oni su se *saznali* preko interneta.(They got to know each other through the internet.)
5. *Saznajmo* nešto novo.(Let's find out something new.)